Lakers’ Ron Artest Suspended for Game 3 of Mavericks Series for Hard Foul

-- B y   M i c h a e l   S i l l u p
-- 
2011-05-05T20:01:37Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-05/lakers-ron-artest-suspended-for-game-3-of-mavericks-series-for-hard-foul.html
The Los Angeles Lakers’  Ron Artest  was
suspended for the third game of his team’s second-round National
Basketball Association playoff series against the  Dallas 
Mavericks for a flagrant foul against J.J. Barea.  The Lakers trail the best-of-seven series two games to
none. Game 3 is scheduled for tomorrow in Dallas.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Michael Sillup at 
 msillup@bloomberg.net  